<item>
            <title>[LU-905] keep BH reference on root node of IAM container</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-905</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;IAM in ldiskfs-osd will always consume some slots in BH LRU (see: fs/buffer.c), if we keep buffer_head reference on root node, we can save one slot in BH LRU and could be somehow helpful for overall performance, I did some tests, LRU hits rate increased 5%-10% while creating files if we always keep this reference.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
